1
00:00:01,210 --> 00:00:03,780
(Episode 63)

2
00:00:03,840 --> 00:00:05,140
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

3
00:00:19,090 --> 00:00:21,930
Come to think of it,
CEO Chae approached me on purpose.

4
00:00:22,230 --> 00:00:25,260
CEO Chae was behind all those times
Jang Mi almost died.

5
00:00:25,860 --> 00:00:28,500
She couldn't let it get out
that Ma Seo Rin and Jang Mi are twins.

6
00:00:28,770 --> 00:00:30,070
That woman...

7
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:33,200
So she stole the twins from my mom
and raised one of them.

8
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:36,710
I won't let her get away with this.
My poor mom...

9
00:00:37,440 --> 00:00:40,910
My mom was so sharp. I bet what happened
to her was all CEO Chae's doing.

10
00:00:41,250 --> 00:00:42,280
That woman.

11
00:00:42,910 --> 00:00:44,080
I won't let her get away with it.

12
00:00:57,730 --> 00:00:58,730
Ma'am.

13
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,430
Oh? Baek Ho's here.

14
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:03,640
I like Baek Ho.

15
00:01:05,070 --> 00:01:08,270
I miss Jang Mi. Jang Mi is so pretty.

16
00:01:08,370 --> 00:01:10,810
Jang Mi really misses you too, ma'am.

17
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:14,780
Tae Pyung and I will be sure
to bring her back.

18
00:01:15,050 --> 00:01:18,220
Tok Hee too. Ok Hee and Tok Hee, okay?

19
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:21,220
Yes. We'll be sure to bring them back.

20
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:23,590
Wait a minute. Mom.

21
00:01:24,060 --> 00:01:25,720
Mom, you kept saying "Ok Hee"
and "Tok Hee,"

22
00:01:26,020 --> 00:01:27,960
were you talking about Jang Mi
and Ma Seo Rin?

23
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:30,800
I like Ok Hee and Tok Hee.

24
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:33,430
Tok Hee is hurt.

25
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:36,430
My mom knew everything all along.

26
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:41,240
Grandma, I finished my drawing.
Let's go inside and play.

27
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:42,510
Okay.

28
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:46,380
Bo Ra is so pretty. Let's go.

29
00:01:49,550 --> 00:01:51,950
What does Jang Mi think
she'll accomplish...

30
00:01:51,950 --> 00:01:53,180
by posing as Ma Seo Rin at Chairman Ma's?

31
00:01:53,650 --> 00:01:55,950
Since CEO Chae is the real culprit
in your father's case,

32
00:01:56,290 --> 00:01:58,560
she's finding proof to make her pay.

33
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,190
Now that we know,

34
00:02:00,330 --> 00:02:02,730
we can't let Jang Mi face CEO Chae alone.

35
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:07,330
If she gets caught,
her life will be in danger.

36
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:10,300
I will never let that happen.
Not with her big brother around.

37
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:21,010
I saw the General Manager leave,
so I assumed you two were done...

38
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:29,250
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

39
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:33,090
You're craftier than you look.

40
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:35,630
You used to be so forward,

41
00:02:35,730 --> 00:02:39,330
but now you know how to pull back
and let a man come to you.

42
00:02:40,060 --> 00:02:41,200
Worry about yourself, Mom.

43
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:44,770
Who sent this?

44
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:54,050
Gosh, why won't it come out?

45
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:29,680
Who is this?

46
00:03:35,050 --> 00:03:37,720
I said, who is this person lying here?

47
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:42,790
- Who is that?
- I'm asking you!

48
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,230
This person looks badly hurt.

49
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:49,370
Why would someone send
a picture like this to you, Mom?

50
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:53,440
You didn't hurt this person, did you?

51
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,970
What are you talking about?

52
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:57,240
What do you take your mother for,
saying something like that?

53
00:03:58,210 --> 00:04:01,250
Why would I ever hurt someone?
For what reason?

54
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:03,280
Then who on earth
would send something like this?

55
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:08,350
What did you see that startled you?
Let me see. What is it?

56
00:04:10,490 --> 00:04:12,260
I don't know what's going on either.

57
00:04:13,060 --> 00:04:14,060
That's it.

58
00:04:14,430 --> 00:04:18,000
Scumbags must be playing
a twisted prank to get money.

59
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,200
That photo must be a deepfake.

60
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:24,270
Is that what it is?

61
00:04:24,900 --> 00:04:27,770
What kind of jerks would pull
a prank like this on my mom?

62
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:32,580
- This doesn't look fake. It looks real.
- Give that to me.

63
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:40,050
Mom, let's report that
to the police right away.

64
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:44,090
I'll report it and find out
what kind of jerks are messing with you.

65
00:04:45,060 --> 00:04:47,260
They need to be taught a serious lesson.

66
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:48,890
Ma Seo Rin.

67
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:51,000
Don't do anything rash.

68
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:52,700
Why not?

69
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:55,230
You said this was a fake, doctored photo.

70
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,100
Why are you so flustered?

71
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,640
Ma Seo Rin.

72
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,670
You are the one who will lead Dream.

73
00:05:03,210 --> 00:05:05,910
- How can you be so shortsighted?
- What?

74
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:09,950
We can't let trashy gossip like this
get out to the media.

75
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:12,250
It could rattle the shareholders,

76
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:16,190
and that could cause
Dream's stock price to drop.

77
00:05:17,090 --> 00:05:18,960
Let this be a lesson to you.

78
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:21,730
How is this just gossip? This is a crime.

79
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:25,260
You're being blackmailed, Mom.

80
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:28,500
Manager Lee and I will handle this matter.

81
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,340
You just stay out of it and go home early.

82
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:33,910
Okay, Mom.

83
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:37,710
But Mom, you know you're
acting weird today, right?

84
00:05:50,690 --> 00:05:55,330
Manager Lee, find the courier
who gave me the documents. Now!

85
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:59,160
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

86
00:06:00,470 --> 00:06:03,370
First the father, now the son?
Doesn't that seem a little strange?

87
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,800
I don't know about this.

88
00:06:05,640 --> 00:06:09,140
Is Director Ma just upset
that I was invited?

89
00:06:10,210 --> 00:06:11,310
That's strange.

90
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:15,380
Did her feelings for me
suddenly fade after the accident?

91
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:19,980
What's this?
Am I actually feeling neglected?

92
00:06:31,260 --> 00:06:33,060
That was definitely a picture of Dad.

93
00:06:33,770 --> 00:06:34,770
That means...

94
00:06:35,130 --> 00:06:38,300
that USB must have a video
from the accident.

95
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:40,610
But who sent it?

96
00:06:41,410 --> 00:06:43,610
Could it have been someone who was
at the scene of the accident?

97
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,750
Who on earth would send me
something like this?

98
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:52,450
That was ages ago.

99
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:56,750
After all this time,
why send this now? Why?

100
00:07:03,290 --> 00:07:04,300
What am I going to do?

101
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,370
This means someone saw
what happened that day.

102
00:07:08,470 --> 00:07:10,000
What if they go to the police?

103
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,270
Don't worry.

104
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,240
The fact that they sent it to you
and not the police...

105
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:16,170
means they must have some other motive.

106
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,840
Money, I'm sure.

107
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:22,480
Then why haven't they called back
to demand the money?

108
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:27,050
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

109
00:07:27,190 --> 00:07:29,850
Yes, it's me. Any news on the courier?
Did you get him?

110
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:34,760
Keep looking.

111
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:36,630
You didn't get him?

112
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:41,970
They must have delivered it in person.
You were supposed to catch them!

113
00:07:43,470 --> 00:07:45,640
I should have acted sooner.

114
00:07:46,370 --> 00:07:47,540
But something's strange.

115
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:52,580
They witnessed it and have it on video,
so why have they been quiet until now?

116
00:07:53,210 --> 00:07:56,350
"Witnessed?" So there was a witness!

117
00:07:56,780 --> 00:08:00,320
That's not the issue.
If this video gets out,

118
00:08:00,450 --> 00:08:03,920
everything I've worked for will be ruined.

119
00:08:04,420 --> 00:08:05,760
I'll be right back, CEO Chae.

120
00:08:06,290 --> 00:08:09,730
- Where are you going?
- They might call, so watch your phone.

121
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,820
(Letter of Explanation, Name: Jin Hong Ju)

122
00:08:54,170 --> 00:08:55,770
Manager Lee.

123
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:58,640
The blackmailer still hasn't called.

124
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:03,950
What was that? Did she say blackmail?
Is CEO Chae being blackmailed?

125
00:09:11,460 --> 00:09:13,060
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

126
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,190
What is it?

127
00:09:14,190 --> 00:09:17,360
I brought my letter of explanation.

128
00:09:17,860 --> 00:09:18,860
Just leave it there and go.

129
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:22,400
- CEO Chae, is something wrong?
- Quiet!

130
00:09:22,830 --> 00:09:23,830
I said, get out!

131
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,100
Yes, ma'am.

132
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:30,410
Here.

133
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:50,190
Where is he going?

134
00:09:56,470 --> 00:09:57,570
The third basement level?

135
00:09:58,370 --> 00:10:01,440
Basement level three.
That's the executive parking lot!

136
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,040
In that case...

137
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,180
Don't tell me.

138
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,710
But something's strange.

139
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:11,820
They witnessed it and have it on video,
so why have they been quiet until now?

140
00:10:23,930 --> 00:10:25,460
Third basement level.

141
00:10:39,980 --> 00:10:41,880
Go and tell them
why you did that to Suk Hee...

142
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,730
(331 H 6332)

143
00:11:50,250 --> 00:11:51,750
This is Manager Lee Kang Hyuk.

144
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,850
Put Assistant Manager Park
from the facilities team on the line.

145
00:11:55,590 --> 00:11:59,920
Hey, Assistant Manager Park.
Which executive parks in spot B3B04?

146
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:01,890
B3B04.

147
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:05,530
So that's who sent the video
and Dad's photo?

148
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,710
Who's threatening
to tell Young Ja about...

149
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:17,480
my meeting with Chae Hwa Young?

150
00:12:20,010 --> 00:12:22,780
Someone who holds a grudge against me...

151
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:29,520
Could it be the late Oh Bok Gil's son?

152
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:33,890
It might just be him.

153
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:35,460
Oh Tae Pyung.

154
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,200
Yes, Professor Kang.

155
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:50,310
I'm not feeling very well right now,
so maybe some other time...

156
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:53,840
About the person
who sent me that strange picture.

157
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:56,180
I have a feeling...

158
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:59,080
it's the son of the man who died,
Oh Tae Pyung.

159
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:03,490
- What?
- The man who died, Oh Bok Gil.

160
00:13:03,990 --> 00:13:05,790
I'm positive it's his son.

161
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,360
All right.

162
00:13:08,890 --> 00:13:11,330
Don't let on to anyone.
Just sit tight for now.

163
00:13:11,730 --> 00:13:12,830
I'll look into it.

164
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,230
Okay, I will.

165
00:13:20,100 --> 00:13:22,870
Honey. The kids aren't home yet, right?

166
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:28,150
- What?
- What should we have for dinner tonight?

167
00:13:31,450 --> 00:13:32,450
Are you listening to me?

168
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:35,090
- Honey.
- What?

169
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:36,750
Yes.

170
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:39,360
Seriously.

171
00:13:40,220 --> 00:13:41,960
Ever since your accident,

172
00:13:42,690 --> 00:13:44,830
it seems like it's really taken a toll
on you.

173
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:48,970
With Jun Ho's wedding coming up,

174
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:51,400
you should get your hair cut...

175
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:54,470
and get a facial to look refreshed.

176
00:13:54,710 --> 00:13:57,440
And I should sign up for Pilates again.

177
00:13:57,510 --> 00:14:00,580
I can't give his future in-laws anything
to criticize at the wedding.

178
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:04,480
What in the world are you talking about?
I told you Jun Ho isn't marrying them.

179
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:07,050
- I made myself perfectly clear.
- Honey...

180
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:08,220
Do you think I'm joking?

181
00:14:09,190 --> 00:14:10,450
Unbelievable.

182
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:26,540
You wanted to see me, CEO Chae?

183
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:30,410
Who did you say delivered
that envelope earlier?

184
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:33,580
It was a courier in a black helmet.

185
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:36,210
They have video evidence...

186
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:39,280
but they're blackmailing me
instead of going to the police?

187
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,750
It can't be Oh Tae Pyung.

188
00:14:42,420 --> 00:14:46,590
He wouldn't sit on the evidence this long
and only start threatening me now.

189
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:48,630
Then again...

190
00:14:49,190 --> 00:14:52,260
I can't be sure.
I should check, just in case.

191
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:54,370
That's all. You can head home.

192
00:14:54,970 --> 00:14:55,970
Yes, CEO Chae.

193
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:57,870
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

194
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:06,510
Director Kim?

195
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:10,380
All right, got it.

196
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:44,350
What am I going to do?

197
00:16:12,310 --> 00:16:13,310
Hello?

198
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:16,650
I'm sorry, who did you say this was?

199
00:16:19,950 --> 00:16:20,950
Oh Tae Pyung.

200
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:23,690
Oh Tae Pyung, what is this about?

201
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,490
You're saying you're here?

202
00:16:30,290 --> 00:16:32,330
Stay right there. I'm on my way.

203
00:16:42,010 --> 00:16:46,010
- We were having a nice time, for once.
- What? How can you be joking right now?

204
00:16:46,280 --> 00:16:49,480
I'm grateful you saved me,
but we could've met at the office later.

205
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:50,850
Why did you come all the way here?

206
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:53,980
I don't want you putting yourself
in danger, Baek Ho.

207
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:55,450
Don't say that, Jang Mi.

208
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:57,920
Are you asking me to lose you
all over again?

209
00:16:58,460 --> 00:16:59,990
You have no idea
what a nightmare that was for me.

210
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:03,090
From now on, I'm staying by your side.

211
00:17:03,430 --> 00:17:06,030
I'm never leaving you alone again. Got it?

212
00:17:10,030 --> 00:17:12,140
I just want to see CEO Chae.

213
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:16,440
Just go. I told you CEO Chae is
out of town on business.

214
00:17:17,940 --> 00:17:18,940
Really?

215
00:17:19,340 --> 00:17:21,580
- I guess it can't be helped then.
- But, Mr. Oh.

216
00:17:22,010 --> 00:17:25,950
You can't keep showing up like this.
CEO Chae is a very busy woman.

217
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:28,290
You can't just show up unannounced
whenever you feel like it.

218
00:17:28,450 --> 00:17:30,750
Okay, I get it.

219
00:17:34,890 --> 00:17:36,260
You can let Manager Lee go.

220
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:40,000
All right, I'm leaving.

221
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:53,480
Did you find anything?

222
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:56,110
This video wasn't recorded
by an eyewitness.

223
00:17:56,450 --> 00:17:59,180
- It's footage from a dashcam.
- A dashcam?

224
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:02,550
- Whose car is it?
- Parking spot B3B04 is...

225
00:18:02,850 --> 00:18:03,920
Director Kim's assigned spot.

226
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:08,430
Are you saying Director Kim has the nerve
to threaten me?

227
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:11,530
No. Director Kim moved to
our Beijing branch a few months ago.

228
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:13,630
He was in Beijing
when that incident occurred.

229
00:18:14,130 --> 00:18:15,130
What?

230
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,600
So you're saying it wasn't
Director Kim's car?

231
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:20,400
It is Director Kim's car, but...

232
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:23,010
Director Kim is in Beijing
on business right now,

233
00:18:23,470 --> 00:18:25,480
but his car is parked here.

234
00:18:26,380 --> 00:18:30,210
How is that possible?
Who would dare pull a stunt like this?

235
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:32,420
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

236
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,520
(Restricted Number)

237
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:38,660
Just a moment.

238
00:18:41,120 --> 00:18:43,630
(Restricted Number)

239
00:18:43,690 --> 00:18:45,630
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

240
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:49,870
CEO Chae Hwa Young,

241
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:53,470
I trust you received the gift I sent.

242
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:56,070
Who are you?

243
00:18:56,770 --> 00:18:58,440
How dare you pull a stunt like this?

244
00:18:58,810 --> 00:19:00,880
You're a bit hot-headed, aren't you?

245
00:19:01,410 --> 00:19:03,550
How about we play a game of 20 questions?

246
00:19:04,380 --> 00:19:07,250
Director Kim put you up to this,
didn't he?

247
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:09,320
Don't play dumb with me.

248
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:10,990
That video is...

249
00:19:11,460 --> 00:19:15,330
- from Director Kim's dashcam.
- You're quick.

250
00:19:15,930 --> 00:19:18,930
Although,
you're barking up the wrong tree.

251
00:19:19,330 --> 00:19:20,800
The wrong tree?

252
00:19:21,870 --> 00:19:22,970
You're saying it's not Director Kim?

253
00:19:23,970 --> 00:19:25,000
Then who is it?

254
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,970
I asked, who is it?

255
00:19:26,970 --> 00:19:29,670
Why don't you take a guess?

256
00:19:30,770 --> 00:19:33,140
Hello?

257
00:19:33,210 --> 00:19:35,410
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

258
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:37,410
Who is it? Who the heck is it?

259
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:11,920
The person you're calling is unavailable.
Connecting to voicemail.

260
00:20:12,780 --> 00:20:15,120
I guess Director Kim
already went home for the day.

261
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:20,590
Chae Hwa Young definitely looked like
she was being blackmailed.

262
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,030
CEO Chae of all people?

263
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:25,760
So you're saying there was a USB
in the envelope with the photos?

264
00:20:25,830 --> 00:20:29,170
It looked like she was watching a video.
I couldn't see what, though.

265
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:32,740
Maybe it was some kind of dashcam footage
from back then?

266
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:34,840
Then we need to find that USB.

267
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:36,270
And this Director Kim character.

268
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:38,880
If he has some sort of grudge
against CEO Chae,

269
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:41,780
it's possible he's
blackmailing her for money.

270
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:44,210
- That's a good point.
- Hey, Jang Mi.

271
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,020
Are you really okay?

272
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,190
You and Baek Ho.

273
00:20:48,850 --> 00:20:50,150
We finally got to see each other
after so long,

274
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:53,120
and I'm sorry I got you
tangled up in this mess.

275
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:55,860
Don't say that. If anything, I'm relieved.

276
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:58,630
I'm just so glad I can be here
with you right now.

277
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:02,200
I will find the evidence we need
to take CEO Chae down for good.

278
00:21:02,530 --> 00:21:03,630
With you by my side.

279
00:21:04,940 --> 00:21:06,940
- Baek Ho.
- Jang Mi.

280
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:09,010
I've got your back.

281
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:16,410
For Mom's sake, don't overdo it.
I can't let anything happen to you, too.

282
00:21:16,510 --> 00:21:19,250
It's for Mom's sake that I have to
make that wicked Chae Hwa Young...

283
00:21:20,450 --> 00:21:22,250
pay for her crimes.

284
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,420
What? She's being blackmailed?

285
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:30,360
Yes, I'm serious. It looks like...

286
00:21:30,630 --> 00:21:35,170
- CEO Chae is being blackmailed.
- Blackmailed?

287
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,440
Isn't this good news?

288
00:21:39,570 --> 00:21:42,310
Who's blackmailing her? Who?

289
00:21:42,710 --> 00:21:45,040
- I told you, I don't know.
- Oh my.

290
00:21:46,210 --> 00:21:49,580
I don't know who it is, but it looks like
she's really in hot water this time.

291
00:21:51,110 --> 00:21:52,580
Serves her right.

292
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:04,490
Something feels off.

293
00:22:05,630 --> 00:22:07,230
What's their endgame?

294
00:22:07,560 --> 00:22:08,570
What is?

295
00:22:10,330 --> 00:22:12,540
What do you think you're doing,
barging into my room like a stranger?

296
00:22:12,540 --> 00:22:13,600
Have you no manners?

297
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,740
Am I "stranger" to you?

298
00:22:17,540 --> 00:22:20,980
So you've been treating me
like a stranger all this time.

299
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,150
Ma Seo Rin.

300
00:22:22,210 --> 00:22:25,950
I did knock. You were probably just
so lost in thought you didn't hear me.

301
00:22:26,850 --> 00:22:28,820
But is that really important right now?

302
00:22:29,050 --> 00:22:32,060
What about the pictures and the USB
you got at the office?

303
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:37,190
Who's blackmailing you?
I'm asking you who is blackmailing you!

304
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:39,600
Ma Seo Rin, keep your voice down!

305
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:42,800
What are you talking about, blackmail?
No one is blackmailing me.

306
00:22:43,230 --> 00:22:44,630
Then why did you look so shocked?

307
00:22:45,170 --> 00:22:48,910
Who was that man collapsed in the picture?
I saw it, you know.

308
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:51,240
Where is that picture?
I need to see it again.

309
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,310
Will you stop it?

310
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:55,580
- Mom.
- What do you take your own mother for?

311
00:22:56,050 --> 00:22:58,450
This kind of thing happens
when you run a business.

312
00:22:58,980 --> 00:23:00,120
Are you even my daughter?

313
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:02,850
Where do you get off
coming at me like this?

314
00:23:03,050 --> 00:23:04,290
You think I'm challenging you?

315
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:06,760
I was just asking because I was curious.

316
00:23:07,420 --> 00:23:10,460
But I have to say,
your reaction is really surprising.

317
00:23:11,330 --> 00:23:12,630
Why are you being so defensive?

318
00:23:13,730 --> 00:23:14,730
Unbelievable.

319
00:23:31,010 --> 00:23:34,380
What on earth could she be
getting blackmailed for?

320
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,650
Gosh, I'm dying to know.

321
00:23:51,940 --> 00:23:52,940
CEO Chae.

322
00:23:53,600 --> 00:23:55,540
Is something on your mind?

323
00:23:56,370 --> 00:23:57,710
You don't look well.

324
00:23:58,580 --> 00:23:59,580
Pardon?

325
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:02,950
He's right. You look terribly pale.

326
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,280
I bet you couldn't sleep much last night.

327
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:08,250
You must've dozed off
and just woken up, right?

328
00:24:08,550 --> 00:24:12,990
If something's bothering you, talk to us.
You're not running this company alone.

329
00:24:13,690 --> 00:24:15,390
Nothing's bothering me.

330
00:24:17,460 --> 00:24:20,630
Oh my, so satisfying and sweet.

331
00:24:21,230 --> 00:24:24,370
Funny, this soup tastes
extra satisfying today.

332
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:26,940
Delicious.

333
00:24:30,810 --> 00:24:31,810
Delicious.

334
00:24:44,150 --> 00:24:45,290
Right, Oh Jang Mi.

335
00:24:46,090 --> 00:24:48,530
That brat Oh Jang Mi,
now that she's awake...

336
00:24:49,330 --> 00:24:51,860
she could be the one
pulling this stunt behind my back.

337
00:24:52,630 --> 00:24:54,900
That would explain
why they're not asking for money...

338
00:24:55,300 --> 00:24:57,000
and are just trying to drive me insane.

339
00:25:02,170 --> 00:25:03,810
I have to find that USB.

340
00:25:05,040 --> 00:25:06,740
The fact that
she was sent Dad's photo means...

341
00:25:07,380 --> 00:25:08,910
that video Chae was watching...

342
00:25:09,450 --> 00:25:11,820
could be the key evidence
of Dad's accident.

343
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:16,390
I will find it and make her pay
for her crimes.

344
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,230
Aren't you going to work?

345
00:25:30,130 --> 00:25:32,000
Don't worry, I'm just about to head out.

346
00:25:33,070 --> 00:25:35,670
Why? Is there something on my face?

347
00:25:36,170 --> 00:25:39,640
I was just wondering whose side you're on.

348
00:25:40,610 --> 00:25:43,610
- What?
- Even if I had stolen something,

349
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:47,320
you're supposed to be on my side,
always and forever, aren't you?

350
00:25:48,220 --> 00:25:49,490
But what's with your attitude?

351
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:51,120
You treat your mother like a criminal.

352
00:25:52,190 --> 00:25:55,030
Seriously?
What nonsense are you talking about?

353
00:25:55,490 --> 00:25:57,260
Of course I'm on your side.

354
00:25:57,590 --> 00:26:01,230
Even if you killed someone,
I'd be on your side.

355
00:26:02,370 --> 00:26:05,400
Don't get upset over nothing.
Now hurry up and get to work.

356
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:08,640
Fine, I get it.

357
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:15,410
Isn't it time for you
to head to the salon?

358
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:24,750
I'll head out first.

359
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:26,390
Okay.

360
00:26:35,700 --> 00:26:37,700
Wait, does Chae Hwa Young
suspect something?

361
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:39,640
I need to be careful.

362
00:26:50,210 --> 00:26:53,320
I'm sure she didn't throw out the USB.
She must have put it somewhere.

363
00:26:54,020 --> 00:26:55,190
I have to find it.

364
00:27:09,870 --> 00:27:13,640
- You just left. Why are you back?
- Yes, I forgot something.

365
00:27:13,940 --> 00:27:15,010
I see.

366
00:27:19,810 --> 00:27:20,810
Gosh.

367
00:28:20,570 --> 00:28:22,040
(The First Man)

368
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:24,810
Who just makes a threat
and doesn't call back?

369
00:28:25,180 --> 00:28:27,010
I'll put a tail on Oh Tae Pyung.

370
00:28:27,210 --> 00:28:30,450
And just in case,
find out if Oh Jang Mi is awake yet.

371
00:28:31,710 --> 00:28:34,080
- Are you all right?
- Are you hurt? Are you okay?

372
00:28:34,650 --> 00:28:37,190
I never knew Seo Rin had that in her.

373
00:28:37,650 --> 00:28:40,390
Tomorrow at noon. They told me
to bring the money and come alone.

374
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:43,730
I'll follow Chae Hwa Young
and try to take the evidence from her.

375
00:28:43,790 --> 00:28:44,790
You will?

376
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:48,260
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
